{"tid":1067231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"古天樂電影《掃毒2》之中環地鐵撞車","createTime":"2019-03-18T11:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T06:58:47.000Z","uid":84633,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5333831c85d41b1936e35b63347011cfad4e0c62","tid":1067231,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"神預告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//【掃毒2】首預告殺入「中環站」 古天樂霸氣造型登場挑機華仔<br />\n<br />\n《掃毒2》首條預告長約1分鐘，並開宗明義揭露故事背景，指黑客竊取了毒品調查科的毒販資料。之後鏡頭一轉，見到由劉德華飾演的富商余順天非常痛恨毒品，指他小時候見到不少癮君子因吸毒導致家破人亡，於是他出一億獎金，務求把香港頭號大毒販殺死。而有趣的是，警方指從沒有公布誰是香港最大毒犯。於是令人聯想到，這次黑客竊取毒品調查科的毒販資料是由余順天幕後指使。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2561777/org/cd13e5ae339b02874545ed91dc62f3ee.png/l0xPnlxfVbBl1r-3gboxETShd0vPagCpuJKSn7iSkp8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2561777%2Forg%2Fcd13e5ae339b02874545ed91dc62f3ee.png%2Fl0xPnlxfVbBl1r-3gboxETShd0vPagCpuJKSn7iSkp8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=5c2383ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2561774/org/aba42709ee071c3d7eb49e25b7a6c91a.png/WT2GDtD0n7e4feEA2lQrQlsV9iN84S7sdzYxTnc2MU4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2561774%2Forg%2Faba42709ee071c3d7eb49e25b7a6c91a.png%2FWT2GDtD0n7e4feEA2lQrQlsV9iN84S7sdzYxTnc2MU4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=970e2f43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"beb638c0f7f3a13f1e298cffcd13a0c1ad666d3c","tid":1067231,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P3bPcI48lhM&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP3bPcI48lhM%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKhjXlokmAnO